{
  "text": "Despite its many benefits, there are still challenges and concerns associated with using GenAI for academic writing tasks, including data privacy, intellectual property, students' over-reliance on automated tools, and plagiarism (Lund & Wang, 2023; Ray, 2023; Tlili et al., 2023).",
